## Key Architecture Decisions
- Combined middleware: next-intl locale routing + Supabase session refresh
- All tables have RLS policies
- Auto-sync trigger: auth.users → profiles on signup
- Back button on all pages except landing page
- Admin link in footer
- MD files kept in /md folder at root; **all .md content must be in English** (translate any Turkish to English)
- Supabase: AI always runs `npx supabase db push` after migrations — never tell the user to push manually

